description:
Parallel world is a game platform based on block chain technology, which includes the core business of online games, technical support, community construction, game asset wallet &exchange.

Parallel world is also a basic game chain. It will use block chain technology to create a block chain game ecosystem in the game subdivision field, use the concept of main side chain to improve game performance and bring good game experience to players. The value circulation of the parallel world is PNC, which is the only pass through the whole ecosystem including the Parallel network integrated game platform, Parallel network development platform, Parallel network game asset exchange and Parallel network decentralized community.
name: Parallel network
